Package com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.presentation.data

This package provides means to convert data into a format which is required by the presentation layer.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISCUIDataConvertor<T>
    Interface to be implemented and registered with the framework, for certain data convertors.
    ISCUIPresentationDataConvertor
    Interface to be implemented and registered with the framework, for presentation data preparation purposes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SCUIDataConversionManager<T>
    Manager class which keeps various convertors, ISCUIDataConvertor, against their name identifiers.
    SCUIDBLocalizedDataConvertor
    Utility class which converts data into its DB Localized value.
    SCUIPresentationDataConversionManager
    Utility manager class which handles conversion of data into a format which is required by the presentation layer.

Package com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.presentation.data Description
